# Resend API key for the contact form
# Sign up at https://resend.com (free tier: 3,000 emails/month)
# 1. Create an account
# 2. Get your API key from the dashboard
# 3. (Optional but recommended) Verify a custom domain so emails come from "you@yourdomain.com"
#    Until you verify a domain, you can only send TO your own address using onboarding@resend.dev
